Future Provincial plans include a 2010 Business Network, anticipated to be oper-

ational later this year. It will include:

tential partners, suppliers and new clients.

• A database of companies that want to do Olympic business.
• An  opportunity  for  companies  to  build  new  business  relationships—to  find  po-
• Ability for companies, including international firms, to post a detailed business 
profile  and  search  listings  to  find  the  business  relationships  they  need  to  do 
business around the Games.

Comment on Tourism Impact for Pacific Northwest 

vestment.

