yourself—about why can’t we host it here in Oregon. 

If  you  want  to  do  that,  the  best  thing  to  do  is  to  start  hosting—
like  become  a  training  center  and  to  start  hosting  those  World 
Cups.  Those  are  the  sorts  of  things  that  demonstrate  to  the  IOC 
